# =============================================================================
# INVESTRA Frontend — Environment Variables Example
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to `.env` for local development.
#
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with `VITE_` to the client bundle.
# NEVER put secrets here — anything in this file ends up in the published JS.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Backend API
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# In dev: requests to /api are proxied to http://localhost:5000 by vite.config.ts.
# In prod: set this to your deployed API URL (e.g. https://api.investra.example.com/api).
VITE_API_URL=/api
